
List of states per mode:
    Mode_Menu_MAIN:
        1: screen bound
        2: waiting for textures
        3: building content
        101: animation start
        101-200: animation
        201: animation end
        250: prepare listener
        300: ready, no selection
        301: selection => list
        302: selection => settings
        303: selection => info
        304: selection => exit
        311: selected => list
        312: selected => settings
        313: selected => info
        314: selected => exit
        501: start selected object
        808: wrong input file occured
        808: wrong input file confirmed
    Mode_Menu_LIST:
